  "texts": [
    "We highlight improvements in sample selection and completion generation.",
    "Performance trends from a 5% to 50% annotating budget are depicted in Figure 4, illustrating the effectiveness of our EGSS method against other selection baselines.",
    "Furthermore, we detail reasoning performance at a 50% annotating budget for our CR completion annotation method and the CoT prompting baseline in Table 1.",
    "From Table 1 we can observe that the EGSS method demonstrates significant performance improvements compared with traditional sample selection baselines for active learning.",
    "For arithmetic reasoning tasks (GSM8K and AQuA), EGSS with CLEAR exhibits a remarkable performance advantage."
  ]
